SUMMARY:Comedy of Love: A Valentine's Day Improv
DESCRIPTION:Looking for a Valentine’s Day plan that’s as unpredictable as love itself? Don’t miss The Comedy of Love – a side-splitting\, heart-throbbing improv show that will have you laughing\, blushing\, and maybe even swooning! Watch as real-life couples from our talented ensemble turn your wild suggestions into unscripted tales of passion\, heartbreak\, and everything in between. Whether it’s your first date or a solo adventure\, this one-of-a-kind night promises endless laughs and plenty of “aww” moments. \nJoin us at our cozy theater nestled by the iconic Gum Wall in the romantic Pike Place Market – because nothing says “love” like comedy in one of Seattle’s most charming spots!
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/comedy-of-love-a-valentines-day-improv-3/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Comedy-of-Love-2026-Poster-small.jpg
END:VEVENT
