UID:10010411-1771011000-1771015500@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:I Saw You: A Comedy with Heart VALENTINE'S SPECIAL
DESCRIPTION:This Valentine’s weekend\, Unexpected Productions turns missed connections into unexpected sparks with a special edition of I Saw U. Inspired by Seattle’s favorite alt-weekly section from The Stranger (and classic Craigslist Missed Connections)\, this hilarious and heartfelt improv show imagines what really happens when those almost-lovers finally meet. \nWatch our performers bring the quirkiest\, sweetest\, and most outrageous listings to life\, taking them from first glance to first date—and beyond. Whether you’re coupled up\, flying solo\, or proudly cynical about love\, you’ll laugh\, cringe\, and maybe even swoon as fantasy collides with reality. \nCelebrate love in all its awkward\, hopeful\, chaotic glory with a night of big laughs\, tender moments\, and romantic surprises—only on February 13 & 14 at the Market Theater in Pike Place Market.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/i-saw-you-a-comedy-with-heart-8-2/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ISAWU_3-big.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260213T213000
