LAST-MODIFIED:20260122T181927Z
UID:10010429-1771018200-1771023600@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:Seattle Theatresports Valentine's Show
DESCRIPTION:Turn Valentine’s weekend into a laugh-fueled date night with Seattle Theatresports\, Seattle’s most electric improv battle—special Valentine’s shows on 2/13 & 2/14. It’s fast\, funny\, and wildly unpredictable\, with your suggestions shaping every moment. \nWelcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comedy experience at Unexpected Productions inside the Market Theater. Two teams of top improvisers go head-to-head in a no-holds-barred comedy showdown—part game night\, part sporting event\, and 100% powered by the crowd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race. Laugh ’til it hurts. \nNo scripts. No safety nets. Just bold choices\, quick thinking\, and joyful chaos. Whether you’re bringing a date\, a friend\, or your own romantic skepticism\, this is Valentine’s weekend with edge\, energy\, and a whole lot of heart. \nFri. & Sat. | 9:30 PM | February 13 & 14Love is unpredictable. Comedy should be too.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-2/2026-02-13/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Theatresports-Yellow-Small.jpg
END:VEVENT
