SUMMARY:I Saw You: A Comedy with Heart
DESCRIPTION:Unexpected Productions brings Seattle’s favorite alt-weekly section\, The Stranger’s I Saw U (and Craigslist Missed Connections)\, to life in a hilarious and heartwarming improv comedy show! Every Friday and Saturday at 7:30 PM\, our talented performers take the quirkiest\, sweetest\, and most outrageous listings and imagine what happens when these almost-lovers actually go on a date…and beyond. \nWhether you’re a hopeless romantic or a hardened cynic\, you’ll laugh\, cringe\, and maybe even tear up as we explore the eternal question: is fantasy really better than reality? Join us for a night of unexpected twists\, unfiltered hilarity\, and a dash of love-inspired chaos.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/i-saw-you-a-comedy-with-heart-8/2026-02-20/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/ISAWU_3-big.jpg
END:VEVENT
